title: Frank Zappa - UnCovered: Second Hand Songs (2015) [C]
description:
A 'Cosmik-Compilation' of songs covered by Frank Zappa and/or The Mothers of Invention. 
Artists covered feature Harvey Hindermeyer and Chauncey Olcott. Don't know them? No worries. FZ did. 
Other covered artists feature Johnny Cash, Jimi Hendrix, Cream, The Police, The Allman Brothers Band, Led Zeppelin and more . . . 



Frank Zappa
